    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Description\n\nIn the default settings for perlpls, there is a root settings option for `perl`.\nhttps://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/blob/master/lsp/perlpls.lua: `settings.perl`\nHowever, the LSP itself has already switched to the root option `pls`.\nhttps://github.com/FractalBoy/perl-language-server#neovim-011-and-newer: `settings.pls`",
